        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>
                <strong>Custom Headers and Footers</strong>: The headers and footers in the exported PDF can be
                customized using the
                <a target="_blank"
                    href="https://ej2.syncfusion.com/aspnetcore/documentation/api/gantt/pdfExportProperties/#header">header</a>
